name: L O S T  CONTROL
description:
And we  showed up all the errors and mistakes.
And said, "I've lost control again".
But we expressed every anxiety in many different ways,
Until we lost control again.
And walked upon the edge of no escape.
And laughed, "I've lost control".

Series : "Portrait of Void"
